# Extra key lines for the bonus pack.
#
# HOW TO USE:
#   1. Copy the line(s) below into the camp's  APIs/keys.example.env
#      (so the example file documents that this key exists).
#   2. Then put the REAL key value into  APIs/keys.env  (the private one that is
#      git-ignored) — NEVER into keys.example.env, and NEVER into your code.
#
# Get a free Groq key at https://console.groq.com  (API Keys -> Create).
# It starts with "gsk_". Don't add a credit card — the free tier is plenty.

GROQ_API_KEY=
